text: Hannah Amuchechi Rueben (born 14 February 1994) is a Nigerian freestyle wrestler. At the 2016 Summer Olympics she competed in the Women’s freestyle -69 kg. In 2020, she won the gold medal in the women's freestyle 65 kg event at the 2020 African Wrestling Championships. ==References== Category:Olympic wrestlers of Nigeria Category:1994 births Category:Wrestlers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Living people Category:Commonwealth Games medallists in wrestling Category:Commonwealth Games bronze medallists for Nigeria Category:African Games silver medalists for Nigeria Category:African Games medalists in wrestling Category:Wrestlers at the 2014 Commonwealth Games Category:Competitors at the 2015 African Games
